'''José Gustavo Angel Ramírez''' (19 March 1934 − 23 February 2013) was a [[Colombian people|Colombian]] [[Roman Catholic]].

Ordained to the priesthood on 7 September 1958, Angel Ramírez was named bishop of the [[Apostolic Vicariate of Mitú]], [[Colombia]] on 19 June 1989 and retired on 17 September 2009.<ref>[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/bangram.html José Gustavo Angel Ramírez]</ref>

