The '''Spiritual Direction of the Muslims of Crimea''' (SDMC) ({{lang-crh|Qırım Musulmanları Diniy İdaresi, QMDİ}}; {{lang-ru|Духовное Управление Мусульман Крыма, ДУМК}}) is the central administrative body for the Islamic faith in [[Crimea]].<ref name="history">{{cite web |url=http://resource.history.org.ua/cgi-bin/eiu/history.exe?&I21DBN=EIU&P21DBN=EIU&S21STN=1&S21REF=10&S21FMT=eiu_all&C21COM=S&S21CNR=20&S21P01=0&S21P02=0&S21P03=TRN=&S21COLORTERMS=0&S21STR=Dukhovne_upra_musulman_Krymu |accessdate=2018-01-01 |title=ДУХОВНЕ УПРАВЛІННЯ МУСУЛЬМАН КРИМУ |language=uk |author=Кирюшко М.І. |date=}}</ref> It was established in 1991.<ref name="history"/>
